			<p>Eden (working title) is a VR survival-horror game, taking place in a mysteriously damaged simulation full of deadly, cunning and adaptive AI abominations.</p>
			<img src="Media/Main/SplineDraw.png">
			<p>The game features an experimental VR user interface system, where buttons are physically simulated objects you can grab. The creator tool uses these aspects to create a fluid and fun interface. The scroll bar can be thrown with momentum, the objects can be selected by grabbing and pulling them out of the screen, and added or removed from the favourites wheel by twisting clockwise.</p>
